Class ViewSessionController.SessionRow

java.lang.Object
main.java.com.team.game.controller.ViewSessionController.SessionRow
Enclosing class:
ViewSessionController
public static class ViewSessionController.SessionRow extends Object
Inner class representing a single table row in the sessions view. Used to bind GameSession data to the JavaFX TableView.
